# AUTO-GENERATED by sdk/game_engine/provisioning/loading_screen.py.
# Do NOT edit by hand -- regenerated on every build from the canonical
# template. Per-game theming flows through res://assets/ui/theme.tres
# (ProgressBar/fill stylebox color), so Claude's creative control over
# the bar accent works without touching this file.
#
# Layout rules baked in (see .claude/skills/godot-loading-screen):
#   R1: wordmark uses explicit anchors symmetric around 0.5
#   R2: bottom band anchored to viewport bottom with NEGATIVE offset_top
#   R3: autoload owns PRELOAD_PATHS + _cache + _busy + calls
#       change_scene_to_packed (not _to_file)

# Filled in at engine provisioning time by walking the game's assets/ and
# scenes/. Ordered small/fast -> big/slow so the bar fills smoothly as
# the slower assets land at the end.
